{"tid":1049053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誤當為《哈利波特》取景地　中國遊客蜂擁澳洲大學「朝聖」","createTime":"2019-03-06T04:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T03:07:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1c12c3ee1a4426bbf0fd7b802d332d9672ca2209","tid":1049053,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"據澳洲媒體近日報道，澳洲悉尼大學一棟哥德式建築物與電影《哈利波特》中的霍格華茲魔法學校相似，有些中國旅遊網站居然訛稱電影就在該處拍攝，藉此推銷旅遊行程，導致大量中國遊客專程造訪「朝聖」。<br />\n其實除了有旅遊網站提供錯誤資訊外，網絡上也流傳不少中文文章聲稱該處就是電影《哈利波特》的取景地。<br />\n澳洲SBS新聞網的報道稱，《哈利波特》電影中的霍格華茲魔法學校其實在英國達勒姆大教堂（Durham Cathedral）取景，而悉尼大學的教學辦公中心四方庭院（The Quadrangle）與達勒姆大教堂有相似之處，故吸引不少中國影迷「朝聖」。實際上這一系列電影從未在澳洲取景。報道又稱，更有旅遊網站將悉尼大學該處描述為《哈利波特》電影的拍攝地點，吸引中國遊客前往參觀。<br />\n一名到該處參觀的中國遊客表示，「導遊告訴我們，這是《哈利波特》的取景地點之一」。另一名中國遊客表示，這所大學的建築因出現在電影《哈利波特》中而「非常有名」，這也是他參觀該處的原因。<br />\n四方庭院建築內的尼克爾森博物館（Nicholson Museum）的一名策展人表示，他注意到近年來到訪悉尼大學的中國遊客數量大幅增加，在2017年到2019年，2月份到訪的中國遊客人數暴增超過4000人，他們往往到博物館前台詢問哪裡是電影《哈利波特》的取景地。<br />\n其實除了相關旅遊網站外，網絡上也流傳不少中文文章聲稱該處就是電影《哈利波特》的取景地，或形容該處貌似電影場境，其中一篇文章更以「哈利波特取景地─悉尼大學」為標題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2513904/org/59d7f28f458c51ce626e8f3ae34c23ae.jpg/nYCSD0ToaYe4fEqJi_nh3EzETa3NSryTUq8tdlKvLXY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2513904%2Forg%2F59d7f28f458c51ce626e8f3ae34c23ae.jpg%2FnYCSD0ToaYe4fEqJi_nh3EzETa3NSryTUq8tdlKvLXY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=08f590fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n悉尼大學的教學辦公中心四方庭院（The Quadrangle）被中國遊客誤認為《哈利波特》電影中的霍格華茲魔法學校的取景地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2513914/org/e393de197c2d0cae1098576a3babb2b2.jpg/MxUC6iz6rUPsaCQRc6zrU3tZSmHXmVXBUlYuB1JWLgc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2513914%2Forg%2Fe393de197c2d0cae1098576a3babb2b2.jpg%2FMxUC6iz6rUPsaCQRc6zrU3tZSmHXmVXBUlYuB1JWLgc&h=6a59b5c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2513909/org/bab9ab65ab7f7abaabd788976d2b8eef.png/dbg5NRAtEsDy0PgTtUHo2LFtpDaEQhQOcouz0nKLs9I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2513909%2Forg%2Fbab9ab65ab7f7abaabd788976d2b8eef.png%2Fdbg5NRAtEsDy0PgTtUHo2LFtpDaEQhQOcouz0nKLs9I&h=d1d497ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2513906/org/02800b5b8f7e997e5bc28ff3d9832d0a.png/T2elW0fM2EhmYFpeNQYAJB2sbj6uQsD6KX8mFil_JhY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2513906%2Forg%2F02800b5b8f7e997e5bc28ff3d9832d0a.png%2FT2elW0fM2EhmYFpeNQYAJB2sbj6uQsD6KX8mFil_JhY&h=6ad21bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2513913/org/95ae887e47375137daefe95e98657a5b.png/9ubkD87s0_jd38RjOW03JaI8aOEolqIQtbOYXrWzmF4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2513913%2Forg%2F95ae887e47375137daefe95e98657a5b.png%2F9ubkD87s0_jd38RjOW03JaI8aOEolqIQtbOYXrWzmF4&h=f70a7d73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e70fb836a0976e0cc58746c97441bdaf1a9947a5","tid":1049053,"uid":52946,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"大陸有咩係真"},{"pid":"e5aa0c1cb4d9fd7c048b860bd1a7991d75a0265a","tid":1049053,"uid":56444,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:09:23.000Z","msg":"輕鬆谷旅遊經濟"},{"pid":"93b3b2484e82c8c86d86ec622d211f0112a10540","tid":1049053,"uid":183219,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:14:12.000Z","msg":"冇文化真可怕"},{"pid":"6d98cc9b76afa93d60f2f9e99a4161e93e5180c1","tid":1049053,"uid":18251,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:33:14.000Z","msg":"返孔子學院朝聖吧啦"},{"pid":"37ace4bb250023723e07b834c835eafa30b7ac38","tid":1049053,"uid":27451,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"無知真係好撚可怕"},{"pid":"11537af0060ac51098674e847293ffac30d877f4","tid":1049053,"uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s